{"word":"ποτνιάομαι","slug":"ποτνιάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ποτνιάομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:Ποτνιάς'><el>Ποτνιάς</el></a>\n<el>(ποτνιάομαι,) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to cry</i> or <i>lament aloud, shriek, howl</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}